auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdDeLSfnoyLFHEF3a6oCtnmz8ivZoHnyLfE0GcmkIwJP6w1QQ/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\nACO/CA offer房統計(睇結果)<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdDeLSfnoyLFHEF3a6oCtnmz8ivZoHnyLfE0GcmkIwJP6w1QQ/viewanalytics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdDeLSfnoyLFHEF3a6oCtnmz8ivZoHnyLfE0GcmkIwJP6w1QQ%2Fviewanalytics&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=7bfc005f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdDeLSfnoyLFHEF3a6oCtnmz8ivZoHnyLfE0GcmkIwJP6w1QQ/viewanalytics</a><br />\n<br />\n往年offer數字<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cYYqAFe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcYYqAFe.png&h=8c057ecf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/17/173207_4181a0a71b9fc8c9fefd63f0678e7a92.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F17%2F173207_4181a0a71b9fc8c9fefd63f0678e7a92.png&h=77702d95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4237b9940507e4e920769429daad62dd739ee736","tid":1180252,"uid":78770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:37:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>RD三部曲</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果收到Acceptance form，但你又唔知點填RD，咁點做好呢？以下係三部曲以供參考：<br />\n<br />\n首部曲：<br />\n首先打去GGO講返你個情況，佢地會教你點填<br />\n<br />\n二部曲 (呢part主要針對ACO，CA做法應該係大同小異，如有遺留或補充歡迎巴絲提供)：<br />\nAssume duty date可以填佢日子<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最遲打後三星期內</span></strong></ins>，notice week<ins><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">最遲填五星期</span></strong></ins>，兩者是但一個超出/兩者超出都要俾supporting document<br />\n<br />\n例子：佢assume duty date係寫6/5，earliest date你可以最遲填27/5，記住你寫呢個日子並唔代表你真係呢日rd，你寫5 weeks佢就會預你係一個月辭職通知，佢收到你張form之後會因應你俾嘅時間再睇下邊班training有位，然後再計返日子，最後email rd日子俾你，確保你夠時間同你舊公司辭職<br />\n<br />\n我可以講埋自己個例子你聽：<br />\n<br />\n21/3收offer<br />\n25/3寄返form (我填咗29/4同5 weeks通知)<br />\n25/4收齊rd email同信 (3/6 rd)<br />\n因為我個case都係一個月辭職通知<br />\n變咗我可以係收到rd嘅第2日，即係26/4就遞信<br />\n我last day就會係25/5，而last day同rd exact date之間嘅buffer就會係一星期<br />\n<br />\n就算你填0-4 weeks通知，佢都係會好似我以上所講情況咁，睇下邊班training有位又就到你日子就fill你入去，所以我建議你首先要問清楚GGO，免得時間上夾唔到日子以添麻煩<br />\n<br />\n三部曲：<br />\n填完RD請寄回或親身遞交正本，同fax返acceptance form比GGO (如果係選擇寄回，建議選擇掛號方式同fax同步進行，以免出現寄失情況)<br />\n<br />\n如有遺漏或補充歡迎巴絲提供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n特別鳴謝 夢醒巴"},{"pid":"ff1a582d9ee703282de51284b69e390093709125","tid":1180252,"uid":86590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T17:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac0221514893d23422f43d1e7c8db59eab7d354","tid":1180252,"uid":86590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T17:01:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c21996174e6734681c9ff93e1c041da363a68c","tid":1180252,"uid":132248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T23:51:31.000Z","msg":"wl 春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e98c78e1840f02ce7c8fa30c39d87d76b0360ab","tid":1180252,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T00:18:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd59dfc6dc773cca291244ae235d7f5202006fe","tid":1180252,"uid":172887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T00:37:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0225a48e9ac276be3b2220811466c32defeda13b","tid":1180252,"uid":193484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T01:02:30.000Z","msg":"癡線 咁快就95<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"